✅ Step 2: Log in to Expo
bash
Copy
Edit
npx expo login
✅ Step 3: Configure EAS
Inside your Expo project folder:

bash
Copy
Edit
eas build:configure
Follow the prompts:

Choose Android

Choose Managed workflow

✅ Step 4: Build APK
To build a debug APK (installable directly):

bash
Copy
Edit
eas build --platform android --profile preview
Or to build a production APK:

bash
Copy
Edit
eas build --platform android --profile production

⚠️ By default, EAS builds an AAB (for Play Store). To get an APK, you need to customize your profile (see below).